content.p: The 2024 Knowledge Exchange and Impact awards took place on Thursday 1 February. Here you can read details of who won in each award category, as well as watch a short video taken at the ceremony. A huge congratulations to all our winners and nominees - you are all exceptional in your chosen field. Watch a short video of the Knowledge Exchange and Impact awards 2024, featuring an interview with Professor Tom Rodden, Pro-Vice Chancellor for Research and Knowledge Exchange Get in touch: research.innovation@nottingham.ac.uk Jubilee Conference Centre Jubilee Campus Triumph Road Nottingham, NG8 1DH
